name: Celestial (Orb)
description: We are all born perfect beings. Our bodies are spiritually flawless, even though there are physical defects. We ourselves are the ones who decide our next spirit to be crippled or to remain perfect. And the tendency of men is to cripple him, by accepting the temptations of those on the left. This work wants to remind us to keep our bodies healthy, whatever the current condition, because our bodies are celestial bodies.
